{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857917677,"sessionID":"ses_286a11efcffeHfT23emAoG4Wgn","part":{"id":"prt_d795fda620010toK1VWKv4qjXt","messageID":"msg_d795f9f26001bR5RaqDS9TU1zC","sessionID":"ses_286a11efcffeHfT23emAoG4Wgn","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_c584c9c5cf324126a02b3421","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-024 — DockerService 封装 — Design\n\n## Overview\n\n`DockerService` (`agentcube/services/docker_service.py`) 是 AgentCube CLI 的 Docker 守护进程交互层，封装 `docker` SDK for Python（`docker>=6.0.0`），提供镜像构建、推送、登录、打标、信息查询和清理能力。它被 `BuildRuntime`（本地 Docker 构建）和 `PublishRuntime`（本地镜像推送至 Registry）直接调用。\n\n**Scope**: 补全 spec 中定义但当前实现缺失的方法（`get_image_info`、`_get_image_info`、`remove_image`），修正与 spec 不一致的签名（`push_image`、`_docker_login_sdk`、`_tag_image_sdk` 的返回值类型），并完善错误处理。\n\n**Size**: M — 约 60 行新增代码 + 签名调整 + 测试覆盖。\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                     CLI Commands                         │\n│  pack │ build │ publish │ invoke │ status               │\n└──────────┬──────────────────────────┬────────────────────┘\n           │                          │\n    ┌──────▼──────┐            ┌──────▼──────┐\n    │BuildRuntime │            │PublishRuntime│\n    └──────┬──────┘            └──────┬──────┘\n           │                          │\n           │  check_docker_available()│\n           │  build_image()           │  check_docker_available()\n           │                          │  _docker_login_sdk()\n           │                          │  push_image()\n           └──────────┬───────────────┘\n                      │\n              ┌───────▼───────┐\n              │ DockerService │\n              │               │\n              │ docker.from_  │\n              │    env()      │\n              └───────┬───────┘\n                      │\n              ┌───────▼───────┐\n              │  Docker SDK   │\n              │  (docker-py)  │\n              └───────────────┘\n```\n\n**Design principles**:\n- 每次方法调用独立创建 `docker.from_env()` 客户端（无状态、线程安全、避免长连接泄漏）\n- 所有公共方法返回 `Dict[str, Any]` 或 `bool`，异常向上传播由 Runtime 层捕获\n- `_` 前缀方法为内部辅助，不供外部直接调用\n\n---\n\n## Component Design\n\n### `DockerService.__init__(verbose: bool = False)`\n\n存储 `verbose` 标志，用于后续可选的详细日志输出（当前实现中 verbose 未主动使用，保留接口以匹配其他 Service 的一致性）。\n\n### `check_docker_available() -> bool`\n\n通过 `docker.from_env()` 创建客户端并调用 `client.ping()`。任何异常（连接失败、权限不足、守护进程未运行）返回 `False`。\n\n**Current**: ✅ 已实现，符合 spec。\n\n### `build_image(dockerfile_path, context_path, image_name, tag, build_args) -> Dict[str, str]`\n\n调用 `client.images.build()` 执行构建，返回包含 `image_name`、`image_id`（short_id）、`image_size`（人类可读格式）、`build_time`（秒数，保留两位小数）的字典。\n\n`build_args` 用于传递代理设置（如 `HTTP_PROXY`/`HTTPS_PROXY`），直接透传给 Docker SDK 的 `buildargs` 参数。\n\n**Current**: ✅ 已实现，符合 spec。\n\n### `get_image_info(image_name: str) -> Dict[str, str]`\n\n获取本地镜像的元信息。公共方法，内部委托给 `_get_image_info`。\n\n返回字典包含：\n- `image_id`: 完整 SHA256 ID\n- `short_id`: 截短的 ID（`sha256:xxxxx`）\n- `size`: 人类可读大小（如 `50.0 MB`）\n- `tags`: 镜像关联的标签列表\n- `created`: 创建时间字符串\n\n**Current**: ❌ 缺失，需新增。\n\n### `_get_image_info(image_name: str) -> Dict[str, str]`\n\n内部实现：通过 `client.images.get(image_name)` 获取 `Image` 对象，从 `attrs` 中提取元数据并格式化。\n\n**Current**: ❌ 缺失，需新增。\n\n### `_format_size(size_bytes: int) -> str`\n\n将字节数格式化为人类可读字符串。阈值：`<1024` → `B`，`<1MB` → `KB`，`<1GB` → `MB`，`>=1GB` → `GB`。\n\n**Current**: ✅ 已实现，符合 spec。\n\n### `push_image(image_name, registry_url, username, password) -> Dict[str, str]`\n\n将本地镜像推送至 Registry。\n\n**Spec 签名**（与当前实现不同）:\n```python\ndef push_image(\n    self,\n    image_name: str,\n    registry_url: Optional[str] = None,\n    username: Optional[str] = None,\n    password: Optional[str] = None,\n) -> Dict[str, str]: ...\n```\n\n**当前签名**:\n```python\ndef push_image(\n    self,\n    image_tag: str,          # 完整标签如 registry.example.com/my-agent:v1.0.0\n    registry_url: str,       # 必填\n    username: Optional[str] = None,\n    password: Optional[str] = None,\n) -> Dict[str, str]: ...\n```\n\n**需要调整**: 将 `push_image` 签名改为 spec 定义的 `image_name` + 可选 `registry_url`，内部逻辑：\n1. 如果提供 `registry_url`，先调用 `_tag_image_sdk` 将 `image_name` 打目标标签\n2. 如果提供 `username` 和 `password`，调用 `_docker_login_sdk` 登录\n3. 调用 `client.images.push()` 推送，流式处理日志（当前未消费 push 返回值中的流式日志）\n4. 返回 `{\"pushed_image\": <full_tag>, \"push_time\": \"<n.nn>s\"}`（spec 要求返回 `pushed_image` 和 `push_time`）\n\n**Current**: ⚠️ 已实现但签名与 spec 不一致，返回值缺少 `push_time`。\n\n### `_docker_login_sdk(registry, username, password) -> None`\n\n通过 `client.login()` 登录 Registry。\n\n**Spec 返回值**: `None`\n**当前返回值**: `bool`（返回 `True`）\n\n**需要调整**: 返回值改为 `None`，失败时让 `docker.errors.APIError` 向上传播。\n\n**Current**: ⚠️ 已实现但返回值类型与 spec 不一致。\n\n### `_tag_image_sdk(source_image, target_image) -> None`\n\n将本地镜像从 `source_image` 打标为 `target_image`。\n\n**Spec 返回值**: `None`\n**当前返回值**: `bool`（返回 `True`）\n\n**需要调整**: 返回值改为 `None`。\n\n**Current**: ⚠️ 已实现但返回值类型与 spec 不一致。\n\n### `remove_image(image_name: str) -> bool`\n\n删除本地 Docker 镜像。成功返回 `True`；失败时记录 warning 日志并返回 `False`。\n\n使用 `client.images.remove(image_name)` 执行删除。捕获 `docker.errors.ImageNotFound` 和 `docker.errors.APIError`，记录 warning 后返回 `False`。\n\n**Current**: ❌ 缺失，需新增。\n\n---\n\n## Data Flow Details\n\n### Build 流程\n\n```\nBuildRuntime._build_local()\n  ├── DockerService.check_docker_available()  → bool\n  └── DockerService.build_image()\n        ├── docker.from_env()\n        ├── client.images.build(path, dockerfile, tag, buildargs)\n        ├── client.images.get(image.id)       → 获取 Size\n        └── return {image_name, image_id, image_size, build_time}\n```\n\n### Publish 流程（local build mode）\n\n```\nPublishRuntime._prepare_local_image()\n  ├── DockerService.check_docker_available()  → bool\n  ├── DockerService._docker_login_sdk()       → None (if credentials)\n  └── DockerService.push_image()\n        ├── docker.from_env()\n        ├── client.images.push(repository, tag, auth_config)\n        └── return {pushed_image, push_time}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Error Handling\n\n| 场景 | 异常类型 | 处理方式 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| Docker 守护进程不可达 | `docker.errors.DockerException` | `check_docker_available()` 返回 `False`；其他方法向上传播 |\n| 镜像不存在 | `docker.errors.ImageNotFound` | `remove_image()` 返回 `False` + warning；其他方法向上传播 |\n| 构建失败 | `docker.errors.BuildError` | 向上传播，由 `BuildRuntime` / CLI `_handle_error` 捕获 |\n| Registry 认证失败 | `docker.errors.APIError` | `_docker_login_sdk()` 向上传播；`push_image()` 向上传播 |\n| 推送失败 | `docker.errors.APIError` | 向上传播，由 `PublishRuntime` / CLI 捕获 |\n| 权限不足 | `docker.errors.APIError` (403) | 向上传播 |\n\n**关键约束**: `DockerService` 本身不打印错误信息或调用 `sys.exit()` — 所有异常向上传播，由 Runtime 层或 CLI `_handle_error` 统一处理。\n\n---\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### 现有测试覆盖（`tests/services/test_docker_service.py`）\n\n| 测试类 | 覆盖方法 | 状态 |\n|--------|----------|------|\n| `TestDockerServiceCheckDockerAvailableRunning` | `check_docker_available` (success) | ✅ |\n| `TestDockerServiceCheckDockerAvailableNotRunning` | `check_docker_available` (failure) | ✅ |\n| `TestDockerServiceBuildImageSuccess` | `build_image` (success) | ✅ |\n| `TestDockerServiceBuildImageWithProxy` | `build_image` (with buildargs) | ✅ |\n| `TestDockerServiceBuildImageFailure` | `build_image` (error propagation) | ✅ |\n| `TestDockerServiceFormatSize*` | `_format_size` (B/KB/MB/GB) | ✅ |\n| `TestDockerService_PushImage_Success` | `push_image` (success) | ⚠️ 需更新断言 |\n| `TestDockerService_PushImage_WithCredentials` | `push_image` (auth) | ⚠️ 需更新断言 |\n| `TestDockerService_PushImage_Failure` | `push_image` (APIError) | ⚠️ 需更新断言 |\n| `TestDockerService_DockerLoginSdk_Success` | `_docker_login_sdk` (success) | ⚠️ 需更新断言 |\n| `TestDockerService_DockerLoginSdk_Failure` | `_docker_login_sdk` (APIError) | ⚠️ 需更新断言 |\n| `TestDockerService_TagImageSdk_Success` | `_tag_image_sdk` (success) | ⚠️ 需更新断言 |\n\n### 需新增测试\n\n| 测试类 | 覆盖方法 | 场景 |\n|--------|----------|------|\n| `TestDockerServiceGetImageInfo` | `get_image_info` | 存在镜像，返回完整元信息 |\n| `TestDockerServiceGetImageInfo` | `get_image_info` | 镜像不存在，抛出 `ImageNotFound` |\n| `TestDockerServiceGetImageInfo` | `_get_image_info` | 内部实现验证 |\n| `TestDockerServiceRemoveImage` | `remove_image` | 成功删除返回 `True` |\n| `TestDockerServiceRemoveImage` | `remove_image` | 镜像不存在返回 `False` + warning |\n| `TestDockerServiceRemoveImage` | `remove_image` | API 错误返回 `False` + warning |\n| `TestDockerServicePushImageSpec` | `push_image` | 新签名：`image_name` + `registry_url` |\n| `TestDockerServicePushImageSpec` | `push_image` | 无 `registry_url` 时直接推送本地标签 |\n| `TestDockerServicePushImageSpec` | `push_image` | 返回 `push_time` |\n\n### Mock 策略\n\n所有测试通过 `patch(\"agentcube.services.docker_service.docker.from_env\")` 模拟 Docker 客户端，不依赖真实 Docker 守护进程。\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n### 签名变更影响分析\n\n`push_image` 签名变更会影响以下调用方：\n\n1. **`PublishRuntime._prepare_local_image()`** (`publish_runtime.py:105`):\n   ```python\n   # Before:\n   result = docker_service.push_image(image_tag, registry_url or \"\", username, password)\n   # After:\n   result = docker_service.push_image(image_tag, registry_url or \"\", username, password)\n   ```\n   调用方传递的第一个参数是完整 `image_tag`（如 `registry.example.com/my-agent:v1.0.0`），在新签名中作为 `image_name` 使用。如果 `registry_url` 为空字符串，不进行重新打标，直接推送。行为兼容。\n\n2. **测试文件** (`test_docker_service.py`): 需更新断言以匹配新返回值（`push_time` 替代 `status`）。\n\n### 返回值类型变更\n\n`_docker_login_sdk` 和 `_tag_image_sdk` 的返回值从 `bool` 改为 `None`。由于它们是 `_` 前缀的内部方法，且调用方不检查返回值（`publish_runtime.py:103` 调用 `_docker_login_sdk` 但未使用返回值），此变更为安全。\n\n### 缺失方法实现要点\n\n**`get_image_info` / `_get_image_info`**:\n```python\ndef _get_image_info(self, image_name: str) -> Dict[str, str]:\n    client = docker.from_env()\n    image = client.images.get(image_name)\n    attrs = image.attrs\n    return {\n        \"image_id\": image.id,\n        \"short_id\": image.short_id,\n        \"size\": self._format_size(int(attrs.get(\"Size\", 0) or 0)),\n        \"tags\": \", \".join(image.tags) if image.tags else \"<none>\",\n        \"created\": attrs.get(\"Created\", \"unknown\"),\n    }\n\ndef get_image_info(self, image_name: str) -> Dict[str, str]:\n    return self._get_image_info(image_name)\n```\n\n**`remove_image`**:\n```python\ndef remove_image(self, image_name: str) -> bool:\n    import logging\n    logger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n    try:\n        client = docker.from_env()\n        client.images.remove(image_name)\n        return True\n    except (docker.errors.ImageNotFound, docker.errors.APIError) as e:\n        logger.warning(\"Failed to remove image %s: %s\", image_name, e)\n        return False\n```\n\n**`push_image` 签名调整**:\n```python\ndef push_image(\n    self,\n    image_name: str,\n    registry_url: Optional[str] = None,\n    username: Optional[str] = None,\n    password: Optional[str] = None,\n) -> Dict[str, str]:\n    import time\n    client = docker.from_env()\n    start_time = time.time()\n\n    if registry_url:\n        # Determine target tag\n        parts = image_name.rsplit(\":\", 1)\n        repo = parts[0]\n        tag = parts[1] if len(parts) > 1 else \"latest\"\n        target = f\"{registry_url}/{repo}:{tag}\"\n        self._tag_image_sdk(image_name, target)\n        push_repo = f\"{registry_url}/{repo}\"\n        push_tag = tag\n    else:\n        parts = image_name.rsplit(\":\", 1)\n        push_repo = parts[0]\n        push_tag = parts[1] if len(parts) > 1 else \"latest\"\n\n    auth_config = None\n    if username and password:\n        auth_config = {\"username\": username, \"password\": password}\n        self._docker_login_sdk(registry_url, username, password)\n\n    client.images.push(push_repo, tag=push_tag, auth_config=auth_config)\n    push_time = time.time() - start_time\n    return {\"pushed_image\": image_name, \"push_time\": f\"{push_time:.2f}s\"}\n```\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-024/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py\">\nERROR [47:40] Argument of type \"str | None\" cannot be assigned to parameter \"name\" of type \"str\" in function \"get\"\n  Type \"str | None\" is not assignable to type \"str\"\n    \"None\" is not assignable to \"str\"\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/tests/services/test_docker_service.py\">\nERROR [96:82] Argument of type \"list[Any]\" cannot be assigned to parameter \"build_log\" of type \"Iterator[dict[str, str]]\" in function \"__init__\"\n  \"list[Any]\" is incompatible with protocol \"Iterator[dict[str, str]]\"\n    \"__next__\" is not present\n</diagnostics>","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py":[{"range":{"start":{"line":46,"character":39},"end":{"line":46,"character":47}},"message":"Argument of type \"str | None\" cannot be assigned to parameter \"name\" of type \"str\" in function \"get\"\n  Type \"str | None\" is not assignable to type \"str\"\n    \"None\" is not assignable to \"str\"","severity":1,"code":"reportArgumentType","source":"Pyright","codeDescription":{"href":"https://github.com/microsoft/pyright/blob/main/docs/configuration.md#reportArgumentType"}}],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/__init__.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/tests/services/test_docker_service.py":[{"range":{"start":{"line":95,"character":81},"end":{"line":95,"character":83}},"message":"Argument of type \"list[Any]\" cannot be assigned to parameter \"build_log\" of type \"Iterator[dict[str, str]]\" in function \"__init__\"\n  \"list[Any]\" is incompatible with protocol \"Iterator[dict[str, str]]\"\n    \"__next__\" is not present","severity":1,"code":"reportArgumentType","source":"Pyright","codeDescription":{"href":"https://github.com/microsoft/pyright/blob/main/docs/configuration.md#reportArgumentType"}}]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-024/design.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-024/design.md","time":{"start":1775857917657,"end":1775857917675}}}}
